  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Cleaner [M.Y World @ Canberra]",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assists the teachers in bathing the children</li><li>Serves food to the children at meal times</li><li>Cleans the offices and the toilets</li><li>Cleans the floor after breakfast, before the children’s nap time, after lunch and after tea time</li><li>Ensures that the floor is dry at all times before children are allowed to walk on it.</li><li>Ensures the cleanliness of the children’s chairs, windows, cubby holes, shelves and shoe racks</li><li>Cleans the tables as and when they are dirty</li><li>Assists teachers in removing mattress covers every Friday and slipping them onto the mattresses every Monday</li><li>Assists other staff in cleaning the mess created by children</li><li>Fills the water trough with water every morning and to empty it in the afternoon</li><li>Controls the usage of toiletries according to the budget given</li><li>Assists in cooking whenever needed</li><li>Carries out any other tasks assigned by the Principal from time to time</li></ul><p>M.Y World @ Canberra is located at 350C Canberra Road #01-223 S(753350).</p>",
